---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/legal.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="pk"
  title="Privacy Policy | Ilaaj AI"
  description="Learn how Ilaaj AI collects, uses, and protects your personal and health information."
  canonical="https://www.ilaaj.ai/pk/privacy-policy"
  keywords="ilaaj AI privacy policy, health data protection Pakistan, telemedicine privacy, medical data security Pakistan, patient data policy"
>
  <main>
    <section class="legal-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-hero__icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-600)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="legal-hero__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-hero__meta">Last updated: May 8, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="legal-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="legal-content">
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>At Ilaaj AI, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We may collect information that you provide to us, including:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Personal information (name, phone number, email)</li>
              <li>Health-related information you choose to share</li>
              <li>Device and usage information</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
              <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
              <li>Ensure the security of our platform</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Artificial Intelligence (AI) Usage</h2>
            <p>Our app uses third-party AI services to provide health responses. We may send user queries, interaction history, and non-identifiable technical metadata to the AI system. We <strong>never</strong> share your name, email, phone number, location, or any personally identifiable information with AI services.</p>
            <p>Before any data is shared with third-party AI systems, we obtain explicit user consent during onboarding.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to provide our services. The following retention periods apply:</p>
            <h3>Account &amp; Profile Data</h3>
            <p>Name, email, and phone number are retained while your account is active and permanently deleted within <strong>30 days</strong> of an account deletion request.</p>
            <h3>Health-Related Data</h3>
            <p>Health information you provide is retained while your account is active and permanently deleted within <strong>30 days</strong> of an account deletion request.</p>
            <h3>AI Interaction Data</h3>
            <p>Queries and interaction history sent to third-party AI services are not retained by us beyond <strong>6 months</strong>, after which data is anonymized or deleted.</p>
            <h3>Device &amp; Usage Data</h3>
            <p>Technical data such as device identifiers, app usage logs, and crash reports are retained for up to <strong>12 months</strong>.</p>
            <h3>Analytics &amp; Session Data</h3>
            <p>Analytics data (Google Analytics, PostHog) is retained for up to <strong>12 months</strong>. Session replay recordings are retained for a maximum of <strong>30 days</strong>.</p>
            <h3>Live Chat &amp; Support Data</h3>
            <p>Support chat transcripts and tickets are retained for <strong>12 months</strong>.</p>
            <h3>Backup Copies</h3>
            <p>Backup copies are retained for up to <strong>90 days</strong> after primary deletion, then permanently purged.</p>
            <h3>Requesting Deletion</h3>
            <p>You may request deletion of your data at any time by emailing <strong>support@ilaaj.ai</strong>. We will process your request within 30 days.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. Contact us at any time to exercise these rights.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section">
            <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-section legal-section--highlight legal-contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@ilaaj.ai">support@ilaaj.ai</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +92-324-819-9663</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
